# PLUGIN BINARIES (if using marketplace plugins with precompiled binaries)
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Some plugins ship with precompiled DLLs - usually fine to exclude
# Plugins/*/Binaries/
# Plugins/*/Intermediate/

